{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_23","type":"command_execution","command":"/bin/bash -lc 'git log --oneline -20'","aggregated_output":"59bd4c1 feat(execution): CAS-retry-safe finalize, remove plan.version fencing (Phase 4)\ncd16906 feat(worker): goal-level lease claim + additive execution dispatch (Phase 3c)\n207bdd3 chore(accelerate): record goal-parallelism-2026-07-22 experiment\n29dcf53 Merge task/phase5-workspace-lock: cross-process goal-merge serialization\n1c97e9d fix(workspace): serialize concurrent cycle-branch merges with a per-cycle flock\nedfee43 Merge task/phase3-goal-lease-schema: Phase 3a/3b goal-lease schema + repository\n9567605 feat(db): add per-goal lease repository\nadbaecf Merge task/phase2-enrichment-fanout: Phase 2 enrichment fan-out\n44a8d90 feat(domain): per-goal promotion reservation (goal-parallelism, part 2 of Phase 1)\n662ee90 fix(app): dependency-ready selection for JIT goal enrichment\n928de51 feat(domain): extract shared dependency-graph service (goal-parallelism prep)\n135d6dd fix: replan recovery domain (#45)\nabd7d71 chore(devcontainer): bubblewrap runtime parity + seccomp profile [DRAFT — needs rebuild] (#38)\nb78b991 fix(runtime): classify pi in-band provider errors (rate limits) instead of masking them as empty success (#16) (#43)\nbfc690a fix(domain): coherent cyclic conversational-replan state (unfreeze #10, #12/#13) (#40)\nfddf6eb fix: live API walkthrough — 8 execution/domain/runtime fixes + findings (#39)\ncfc352f fix(runtime): task prompt uses the run role (TDD stage), not the agent's static role (Bug B) (#44)\nfa5304b feat(api): live SSE stream of an attempt's raw runtime output (#37)\nd8b9761 docs: reconcile CLAUDE.md + docs to the cyclic lifecycle; accelerate bookkeeping (#36)\nd7580ec feat: Accelerate run 2026-07-20: env scrub, SSE stream test, docs catch-up, roadmap fold (#35)\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
