{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_70","type":"agent_message","text":"Implemented and committed as `a27923f` (`test(dispatcher): cover goal enrichment routing`). Worktree is clean and `TASK.md` is deleted.\n\nAdded [test_plan_dispatcher.py](/tmp/agent-orchestrator-goalparallel-phase6/backend/tests/unit/orchestration/test_plan_dispatcher.py) with dual memory/SQLite coverage:\n\n- Blocked head plus ready later goal invokes planning, proving lines 89–94 use all ready goal IDs.\n- Enriched goals invoke the runner—not planning—proving the line 95 execution fallback.\n- Missing planning handler returns `PAUSED`, covering lines 91–93.\n- All-terminal cyclic goals fall through line 95 and open a cycle-completion review gate.\n\nVerification output:\n\n```text\nuv run ruff check src tests --fix\nAll checks passed!\n\nuv run mypy src\nSuccess: no issues found in 155 source files\n\nuv run pytest -m \"not integration\" -q\n336 passed, 1 skipped, 223 deselected, 2 warnings in 12.29s\n\nuv run pytest -m integration -q\n219 passed, 4 skipped, 337 deselected, 2 warnings in 137.85s\n```\n\nGraphify refreshed successfully: 5,229 nodes, 15,510 edges, 270 communities. HTML was safely skipped because the graph exceeds the 5,000-node visualization limit."}}
